data.description: Absolutely charming 3 Bedroom 2 Bath split-level, recently renovated! This home sits in a quiet cul-de-sac. Features include sunken family room, separate dining room, and a separate living room. There is beautiful new LVP flooring in the living room, dining room, kitchen and foyer. There has been some painting, and motorized garage doors have been added. Additional features include a 2-car garage and a backyard patio. Don't miss this opportunity! Great home, great schools, great location! This home is being sold As Is.
